name: 2.0.0-M1
body:
Update used dependencies including minimal supported Java version.

- Minimal supported Java version is now 11.
- Camunda version used for JDBC polling is now 7.15.0.

**Release with new implemented GitHub Workflow**

- Add wf0_release.yml to build and push to AWS ECR on release events
- Docker Images now available on [AWS ECR](https://gallery.ecr.aws/viadee/camunda-kafka-polling-client)

[_No code changes have been made compared to the 11 May release with tags v1.2.5 and 1.2.5._]

Update dependencies:

* commons-io -> 2.7
* jackson -> 2.9.10
* jackson databind -> 2.9.10.7
Details regarding changes are available with the [corresponding project](https://github.com/viadee/camunda-kafka-polling-client/projects/7).

Update dependencies for security reasons.

See https://github.com/viadee/camunda-kafka-polling-client/pull/56
Details regarding changes are available with the [corresponding project](https://github.com/viadee/camunda-kafka-polling-client/projects/6).

New features are:
- Polling of task comments
